{
  "stem": "2833.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I kept telling everybody, be careful, because you know the Czech people eat a lot of [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] goose fat.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They brought bread with goose fat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this, on the-- our stomachs, absolutely impossible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because even when we were in Mauthausen, one of the ladies didn't listen and ate soup, which they meant well.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They took from whatever they found from the Germans left over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was peas and beans and-- what they ate, not our food-- and made sort of a one-pot thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I told them, don't eat that, because we can't take it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Our stomach can't take beans and peas.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was-- they found some bacon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They had cut into it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, for heaven's sake don't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that one woman didn't listen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she ate it and ate it and loved it, and then she died, same day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because she was just couldn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we went by train I said, dry bread, dry tomatoes-- potatoes, and anything that is not fat and not heavy we can eat.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But otherwise, you have to be very careful.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They meant very well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They wanted to give us whatever they had saved, you know, under the counter during the war and hidden away, and with butter and with fat.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we got to Prague and it was like 2:00 or 3:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And well, my husband I didn't find anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went and looked, talked to hundreds of people and to the Red Cross and to the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then I found out exactly what happened, where he was killed, when, and his brother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And his parents and sister I had kept in Theresien.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When I left, I had the possibility, so I picked them up and they went home to Olmutz.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
